title: Fela Kuti- (1999) The best best of Fela Kuti  Projeto Chernobyl
description:
The Best Best of Fela Kuti is a compilation album by Nigerian Afrobeat artist Fela Kuti, released in 1999. It was released in the United States in 2000 as part of a reissue series of Kuti's albums. The album was reissued as The Best of the Black President in 2009 by Knitting Factory Records and received universal acclaim from music critics.
